Need a bunch of system packages:

    sudo dnf install htop tmux java-1.8.0-jdk opencv-python3 \
                     python3-virtualenv python3-pip python3-pyserial \
                     python3-devel python3-numpy

    sudo pip3 install inputs


Also need to add own user to `dialout` user group to allow access to Arduino
over serial:

    sudo gpasswd -a `whoami` dialout


